      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric induction. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate selection, complemented by a factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. Meticulously maintained, this unit has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its original kinematic integrity, paired with Electronic Damper Control for optimized transient response. Zero subframe cracks or VANOS issues; this is a mechanically flawless example of BMW M's high-revving heritage.",
